{"tid":965104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞推兩星期優惠 首日$10九件麥樂雞","createTime":"2019-01-01T19:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T16:24:38.000Z","uid":3189,"like":10,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"caff95e06bf59dd7df7d15f1b8e3a0a4127eb7bf","tid":965104,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181231/_2018123122465973845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181231%2F_2018123122465973845.jpg&h=80bf434c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019-01-01 00:01<br />\n<br />\n踏入新一年，香港麥當勞部份產品將於1月2日凌晨起加價5毫或1元。另外同步一連14日推出優惠，首日推出的優惠為$10 九件麥樂雞。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞由1月2日(周三)起，推出「14日限時好戲派」，首4日推出的優惠美食分別為: $10 九件麥樂雞 (1月2日)、$10兩個豬柳漢堡 (1月3日)、$10雙牛芝堡 (1月4日)、$10焦糖蛋糕 OREO 麥旋風 (1月5日)。<br />\n<br />\n另外，麥當勞由1月2日凌晨4時起，部份產品加價5毫或1元。超值早晨套餐、超值套餐、開心樂園餐加1元；單點食品及飲品 (甜品除外) 加5毫。McCafe的單點食品及飲品 加5毫、滋味Combo加1元（詳見另稿）。"},{"pid":"13dc0f73625131fb568b334dd860b7b9b5c04a5e","tid":965104,"uid":61443,"like":216,"dislike":4,"score":212,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:14:04.000Z","msg":"加咗價驚民憤<br />\n然後清倉底貨平息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a629f583bfbe482b91785a87ec23610e47d82d4f","tid":965104,"uid":35382,"like":239,"dislike":3,"score":236,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2tB8F4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2tB8F4.jpg&h=6bd3d842&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09cda9d0277024d4fe2e79711bceab39728b58c9","tid":965104,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":67,"score":-65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T19:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/w600/201812/20190101123007_1_10.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2Fw600%2F201812%2F20190101123007_1_10.JPG&h